WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.141 --> 00:00:00.581
Hi.

00:00:00.941 --> 00:00:02.541
Welcome to the reentry assistant.

00:00:03.141 --> 00:00:05.341
To ensure you're set up for success, here

00:00:05.341 --> 00:00:07.221
are a few grounding instructions.

00:00:07.701 --> 00:00:10.501
This intake is designed to help NDCS

00:00:10.501 --> 00:00:12.781
staff learn more about your reentry

00:00:12.781 --> 00:00:14.541
goals, plans and needs.

00:00:14.981 --> 00:00:16.861
This helps them understand the best way

00:00:16.861 --> 00:00:19.181
to support you as you transition back

00:00:19.181 --> 00:00:20.094
into the community.

00:00:20.394 --> 00:00:22.074
As you answer the following questions,

00:00:22.074 --> 00:00:23.954
you will be interacting with a chatbot,

00:00:24.581 --> 00:00:25.781
not a live person.

00:00:26.381 --> 00:00:28.221
The questions will cover topics related

00:00:28.221 --> 00:00:29.068
to education,

00:00:29.068 --> 00:00:31.181
education, employment, criminal history,

00:00:31.261 --> 00:00:34.341
finances, family and marital details,

00:00:34.621 --> 00:00:36.821
housing, leisure and recreation and

00:00:36.821 --> 00:00:37.861
alcohol and drugs.

00:00:38.381 --> 00:00:40.021
Your responses to this intake will be

00:00:40.021 --> 00:00:42.501
visible only to NDCS staff.

00:00:42.821 --> 00:00:44.661
Information you share will be used to

00:00:44.661 --> 00:00:46.701
assess your needs, not to create

00:00:46.701 --> 00:00:47.941
misconduct reports.

00:00:48.581 --> 00:00:49.701
A few important notes.

00:00:49.928 --> 00:00:51.928
This intake will take about 45 minutes to

00:00:51.928 --> 00:00:52.448
complete.

00:00:52.888 --> 00:00:54.688
Some questions might require careful

00:00:54.768 --> 00:00:57.048
thought. Feel free to pause and reflect

00:00:57.048 --> 00:00:57.928
as much as you need.

00:00:58.528 --> 00:01:00.728
Your progress is automatically saved, so

00:01:00.728 --> 00:01:02.608
you can leave the intake chat and return

00:01:02.608 --> 00:01:03.968
later if you need to pause.

00:01:04.608 --> 00:01:06.608
This intake should be completed before

00:01:06.608 --> 00:01:08.648
your reentry to help develop a plan.

00:01:09.008 --> 00:01:10.838
The sooner you can finish it, the better.

00:01:11.488 --> 00:01:11.848
Now,

00:01:12.288 --> 00:01:13.368
let's get ready to start.

00:01:13.928 --> 00:01:15.928
Press start intake to begin.
